Salvage and Loss at Delta Fish Facilities Metadata
Data column availability is linked to species, adipose fin clip status, and water year.
'Length Row ID' is not static and is not unique in this context. It is for verification purposes with the Salvage Access DB.
Citation: Columbia Basin Research, University of Washington. (2025). SacPAS Loss and Salvage Detail. Available from www.cbr.washington.edu/sacramento/data/query_loss_detail.html.
